></meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Let <tex>{ \mathopen {} \left ( P,C \right ) \mathclose {}}</tex> be a <link href="jms-00A5.xml" type="local" title="Constructive domain theoretic models of linear type theory">dcpo presentation</link> and let <tex>A</tex> be a dcpo; a monotone map <tex>{ P } \xrightarrow {{ f }}{ D }</tex> is said to <em>preserve covers in <tex>C</tex></em> when for all <tex>a \lhd _C U</tex> we have <tex>fa  \sqsubseteq   \bigsqcup _{x \in  U} fx</tex>.</p></mainmatter> </tree></backlinks> <references/></backmatter></tree>